1
00:01:17,480 --> 00:01:18,280
Master Ai.

2
00:01:19,680 --> 00:01:21,920
Thank you for saving me, Master Ai.

3
00:01:22,160 --> 00:01:25,520
I apologize for offending you earlier.

4
00:01:27,240 --> 00:01:28,840
The Day of Sacrifice is fast approaching.

5
00:01:28,840 --> 00:01:31,400
You shouldn't let your guard down, Master Wang.

6
00:01:32,440 --> 00:01:33,400
I know.

7
00:01:33,920 --> 00:01:34,840
I know that.

8
00:01:35,680 --> 00:01:39,680
Master Wang, the Sacrifice you prepared is the fifth wife, right?

9
00:01:39,920 --> 00:01:44,400
It seems I can't hide anything from you, Master Ai.

10
00:01:45,760 --> 00:01:49,200
So having money and power really means you can do whatever you want.

11
00:01:52,080 --> 00:01:54,360
But I still need to warn you.

12
00:01:54,480 --> 00:01:56,040
You must watch out for someone.

13
00:01:58,040 --> 00:02:01,120
You mean Zheng Yu.

14
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:14,320
These herbs can reduce inflammation and stop the bleeding.

15
00:02:14,480 --> 00:02:15,640
But it will hurt a bit.

16
00:02:16,320 --> 00:02:17,320
Just bear with it.

17
00:02:33,440 --> 00:02:35,960
You got hurt because of me.

18
00:02:40,240 --> 00:02:41,400
What?

19
00:02:41,960 --> 00:02:43,800
Are you worried about me?

20
00:02:52,600 --> 00:02:53,520
It's fine.

21
00:02:54,960 --> 00:02:56,840
It doesn't hurt anymore.

22
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:02,720
Wang Shengchang has returned.

23
00:03:02,920 --> 00:03:06,440
And the Day of Sacrifice is only two days away.

24
00:03:06,800 --> 00:03:07,560
When the time comes,

25
00:03:08,120 --> 00:03:10,880
Wang Shengchang will offer you as a Sacrifice to that monster.

26
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,840
You know everything.

27
00:03:17,480 --> 00:03:18,280
Xu Nan,

28
00:03:19,400 --> 00:03:20,360
come with me.

29
00:03:21,160 --> 00:03:22,920
It's too dangerous to stay here.

30
00:03:24,880 --> 00:03:25,880
I won't leave.

31
00:03:26,400 --> 00:03:27,160
If I leave,

32
00:03:27,160 --> 00:03:28,680
there will be another victim.

33
00:03:29,320 --> 00:03:32,440
I must end this sacrifice with me.

34
00:03:32,440 --> 00:03:34,160
But you will really die if you stay here.

35
00:03:34,160 --> 00:03:34,800
You know that, right?

36
00:03:34,800 --> 00:03:35,880
I'm not leaving.

37
00:03:48,040 --> 00:03:48,840
Fine.

38
00:03:49,600 --> 00:03:51,200
Since you insist on staying here,

39
00:03:51,760 --> 00:03:52,640
I will stay with you.

40
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:58,760
I'll go meet that Master Ai tomorrow.

41
00:04:06,520 --> 00:04:10,000
But no matter what happens in the future,

42
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:12,920
promise me you won't push me away again.

43
00:04:17,600 --> 00:04:20,200
Silly girl, why are you crying?

44
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:30,200
I keep hurting you over and over,

45
00:04:32,480 --> 00:04:34,440
but why are you still so good to me?

46
00:04:38,080 --> 00:04:39,400
Because I like you.

47
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,600
In this lifetime,

48
00:04:43,520 --> 00:04:45,320
you are the only one I'll ever love.

49
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,360
Actually, in my heart,

50
00:04:50,680 --> 00:04:52,000
I've always had feelings for you.

51
00:04:52,880 --> 00:04:53,680
But...

52
00:05:38,120 --> 00:05:38,920
Yah!

53
00:05:40,640 --> 00:05:41,400
Yah!

54
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:42,520
Yah!

55
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:46,880
Yah!

56
00:05:49,640 --> 00:05:50,440
Yah!

57
00:05:56,080 --> 00:05:57,640
Zheng Yu! Zheng Yu!

58
00:05:59,520 --> 00:06:00,320
Fatty! Yah!

59
00:06:01,200 --> 00:06:01,960
Sister-in-law!

60
00:06:02,280 --> 00:06:03,600
Yah! Let go of me!

61
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:06,080
Sister-in-law, Zheng Yu arranged all this!

62
00:06:06,080 --> 00:06:07,080
Sit back down quickly!

63
00:06:07,080 --> 00:06:08,720
Let me go! Until we leave Nanwan Town,

64
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,800
I have to treat you roughly for now!

65
00:06:09,800 --> 00:06:11,200
Go back and sit down! Yah!

66
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:30,280
These hand bones...

67
00:06:35,240 --> 00:06:36,560
Those are my mother's remains.

68
00:06:36,840 --> 00:06:38,880
Earlier, I wanted to find someone to relocate her grave.

69
00:06:38,880 --> 00:06:41,200
But I haven't found a good feng shui spot to bury her yet.

70
00:06:41,200 --> 00:06:42,960
It seems in a hundred-mile radius, besides me,

71
00:06:43,320 --> 00:06:44,920
there's someone else who collects bones.

72
00:06:45,680 --> 00:06:47,080
Since Master Ai is so good at reading feng shui,

73
00:06:47,360 --> 00:06:49,600
why did you trick Xu Nan into going to the mass grave?

74
00:06:51,120 --> 00:06:53,760
Did she find her sister's remains?

75
00:06:55,160 --> 00:06:57,840
There were also many other young girls' remains in that place.

76
00:06:58,360 --> 00:06:59,960
Secretly, how many atrocious deeds

77
00:06:59,960 --> 00:07:01,840
have you helped the Wang family commit?

78
00:07:01,920 --> 00:07:02,880
Brother Zheng Yu,

79
00:07:02,880 --> 00:07:04,440
you are wrongfully accusing me.

80
00:07:04,480 --> 00:07:05,880
I only read feng shui.

81
00:07:06,040 --> 00:07:07,640
Nothing else has anything to do with me.

82
00:07:08,800 --> 00:07:10,680
Then how do you explain these?

83
00:07:14,120 --> 00:07:15,920
You are working for Wang Shengchang.

84
00:07:16,160 --> 00:07:18,480
You must know he plans to sacrifice Xu Nan, right?

85
00:07:20,000 --> 00:07:20,760
Of course.

86
00:07:21,160 --> 00:07:23,760
But do you think by sending Zhao Xu Nan away,

87
00:07:23,960 --> 00:07:25,520
Wang Shengchang will have no other options?

88
00:07:26,200 --> 00:07:27,120
What do you mean?

89
00:07:27,720 --> 00:07:29,840
You underestimate him too much.

90
00:07:49,800 --> 00:07:50,800
What's wrong?

91
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:56,040
Master Ai really can predict everything.

92
00:07:56,680 --> 00:07:57,400
Seize him!

93
00:08:11,160 --> 00:08:13,160
You're awake. You must be hungry.

94
00:08:14,160 --> 00:08:15,680
Come and have some noodles.

95
00:08:16,520 --> 00:08:17,920
I cooked them myself just for you.

96
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:24,160
Look at me, Master Ai, how can I eat like this?

97
00:08:24,280 --> 00:08:25,440
Why don't you feed me?

98
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:26,680
Sure.

99
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:35,440
Is Master Ai left-handed?

100
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:39,440
You are rather different.

101
00:08:39,920 --> 00:08:42,320
The first thing others ask when they wake up is

102
00:08:42,440 --> 00:08:43,400
why did you seize me,

103
00:08:43,400 --> 00:08:44,400
let me go.

104
00:08:45,520 --> 00:08:47,520
But you care about my hand instead.

105
00:08:47,520 --> 00:08:48,840
How very interesting.

106
00:08:50,600 --> 00:08:53,280
Then say something more interesting, Master Ai.

107
00:08:53,560 --> 00:08:55,200
How did you plan all this?

108
00:08:56,720 --> 00:09:00,160
Aren't you afraid you'll die after knowing?
